name: nicotinamide-nucleotide amidase
classes: Acting on carbon-nitrogen bonds, other than peptide bonds;
reaction: beta-nicotinamide D-ribonucleotide + H2O = beta-nicotinate D-ribonucleotide + NH3 [RN:R02322]
comment: Also acts more slowly on beta-nicotinamide D-ribonucleoside.

references.title: Purification and properties of nicotinamide mononucleotide amidohydrolase from Azotobacter vinelandii.
